{"name":"余弦相似度","slug":"余弦相似度","count":1,"postlist":[{"title":"数据分析算法-余弦相似度算法原理与实现","uid":"8233a68f529649722ff03871931eba83","slug":"专业基础/大数据/数据分析算法-余弦相似度算法原理与实现","date":"2021-09-27T02:20:59.000Z","updated":"2021-09-27T08:36:01.534Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/专业基础/大数据/数据分析算法-余弦相似度算法原理与实现.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://zjpicture.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/20210926220226.png","text":" 余弦相似度简述 余弦距离，也称为余弦相似度，是用向量空间中两个向量夹角的余弦值作为衡量两个个体间差异的大小的度量。余弦值越接近1，就表明夹角越接近0度，也就是两个向量越相似，这就叫&quot;余弦相似性&quot;。 两个向量a,b的夹角很小可以说a向量和b向量有很高的的相似性...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.9k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"专业基础","slug":"专业基础","count":26,"path":"api/categories/专业基础.json"},{"name":"大数据","slug":"专业基础/大数据","count":4,"path":"api/categories/专业基础/大数据.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"大数据","slug":"大数据","count":8,"path":"api/tags/大数据.json"},{"name":"机器学习算法","slug":"机器学习算法","count":2,"path":"api/tags/机器学习算法.json"},{"name":"余弦相似度","slug":"余弦相似度","count":1,"path":"api/tags/余弦相似度.json"}],"author":{"name":"ZestJourney","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://zjpicture.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/20210822091020.jpg","link":"/","description":"吾好梦中读书~","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"QQ":{"icon":"/svg/qq.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092319.jpg"},"WeiXin":{"icon":"/svg/weixin.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/zhangjie0524/picgo/raw/master/20210822092515.png"},"Github":{"icon":"/svg/github.svg","link":"https://github.com/zestaken"}}}}}]}